<span id="freeTextContainer12481357235670100738">This book sheds light on various aspects of the city of Makkah.<br/>It begins with a discussion of <br/>1. The sacred nature of Makkah Al-Mukarramah,<br/>2. the boundaries of Haram (Sanctuary) and its sanctity<br/>Then it discusses 3. The superiority of Makkah and narrates Ahadith to that effect.</span>

