<li class='cover' id='bookCover_7184066'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7184066-fault-lines"><img alt="Fault Lines: How Hidden Fractures Still Threaten the World Economy" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1383123119l/7184066._SX98_.jpg" />
