<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/12158486.Safiur_Rahman_Mubarakpuri"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1587635035p3/12158486.jpg);'></div>
